# Specify files that shouldn't be modified by Fern
README.md
banner.png
changelog.md

# WireMock stubs for /ecommerce/attribution/metrics were generated with RFC3339_EXTENDED
# datetime format (.000Z) but the PHP serializer uses RFC3339 (Z). The equalTo matchers
# would never match, causing BrevoApiException in CI. Fixed to use Z without milliseconds.
# Protected until Fern fixes the datetime format inconsistency in the PHP generator.
wiremock/wiremock-mappings.json
